    <title>GitHub Hexo报错汇总</title>
    <url>/2020/06/03/github-hexo-bao-cuo-hui-zong/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="hexo-init-网络问题初始化失败"><a href="#hexo-init-网络问题初始化失败" class="headerlink" title="$ hexo init 网络问题初始化失败"></a><code>$ hexo init</code> 网络问题初始化失败</h1><pre><code>删除所有hexo安装包以后重新输入`$ npm intall -g hexo-cli`失败

尝试`$ npm intall -g --foece hexo-cli`成功, `--force` 可以暴力覆盖

其实`$ hexo init`不需要重装hexo-cli服务</code></pre><a id="more"></a>

<h1 id="重置链接"><a href="#重置链接" class="headerlink" title="重置链接"></a>重置链接</h1><p>   <code>npm set registry http://registry.npmjs.org/</code></p>
<h1 id="Porkbun域名提供商DNS设置备份"><a href="#Porkbun域名提供商DNS设置备份" class="headerlink" title="Porkbun域名提供商DNS设置备份"></a>Porkbun域名提供商DNS设置备份</h1><pre><code>https://www.notion.so/7b7de4fac9224d1e9e95cec6e64855c3</code></pre><h1 id="一段插曲"><a href="#一段插曲" class="headerlink" title="一段插曲"></a>一段插曲</h1><pre><code>Hi, sorry, i must hv done something wrong.
i tried to point [shukangzhang.com](http://shukangzhang.com/), which i hv just bought from you, to[shukangzhang.github.io](http://shukangzhang.github.io/). But now when i type [shukangzhang.com](http://shukangzhang.com/), the browser shows a

邮件写到一半，结果网页自动刷新，一切正常了。。。应该是Domain提供商反应比较慢，现在好了</code></pre><h1 id="hexo-deploy-not-found-git"><a href="#hexo-deploy-not-found-git" class="headerlink" title="hexo deploy not found git"></a>hexo deploy not found git</h1><p>   是因为没有装<code>$ npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</code></p>
<h1 id="TypeError-Cannot-read-property-‘replace’-of-null"><a href="#TypeError-Cannot-read-property-‘replace’-of-null" class="headerlink" title="TypeError Cannot read property ‘replace’ of null"></a>TypeError Cannot read property ‘replace’ of null</h1><p>   实在是悲剧，找不到原因，只好$ hexo init 从头来过，哭哭<br>   切记每步操作完一定要$ hexo g&amp;d</p>
<h1 id="FATAL-Cannot-read-property-‘replace’-of-null"><a href="#FATAL-Cannot-read-property-‘replace’-of-null" class="headerlink" title="FATAL Cannot read property ‘replace’ of null"></a>FATAL Cannot read property ‘replace’ of null</h1><p>   是因为config文件里的url: 后面被删掉了</p>
<h1 id="hexo-更改本地路径"><a href="#hexo-更改本地路径" class="headerlink" title="hexo-更改本地路径"></a>hexo-更改本地路径</h1><p>   a. config.yml文件中配置如下：<br>   b. hexo s -p 5000</p>
<h1 id="添加gitalk"><a href="#添加gitalk" class="headerlink" title="添加gitalk"></a>添加gitalk</h1><p>   我原来看的教程推荐的是gitment，结果gitment已经停止服务了，<code>NexT</code>也已经不再集成gitment服务，于是转为安装gitalk评论系统，基于github issues，这里就不过多介绍了，总之，每篇文章都会在你事先建好的Repository里添加一条issues用于保存与这篇文章有关的评论。</p>
<p>   真可谓一波三折，因为很多gitalk安装教程都已经是很旧的了，各种index.md文件找不到啦，comments.swig打开跟教程里不一样啦，comments.ejs语法略有不同啦，折腾来折腾去不知道怎么办。</p>
<p>   还好我有点html基础，发现主题配置文件里_config.yml里直接就有gitalk的相关配置，那我又已经<code>npm i --save gitalk</code>，建好OAuth apps以后，填好各项配置如下:<br>   </p><figure class="highlight"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">gitalk:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  github_id: shukangzhang # GitHub repo owner</span><br><span class="line">  repo: pinglun # Repository name to store issues</span><br><span class="line">  client_id: 59xxxxxx # GitHub Application Client ID</span><br><span class="line">  client_secret: 81xxxxx # GitHub Application Client Secret</span><br><span class="line">  admin_user: shukangzhang # GitHub repo owner and collaborators, only these guys can initialize gitHub issues</span><br><span class="line">  distraction_free_mode: true # Facebook-like distraction free mode</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><br>   模块就添加成功啦<p></p>
<p>   这里必须得提一下我也遇到了老生常谈的<code>Error: Not found</code>的问题，但我的问题比较轻，是因为对别人教程的理解问题，我通过api.github.com查询了我的github_ID，我以为是要填写ID一栏显示的000000那串数字，结果一直Error: Not found，按F12审查元素:<br>   </p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">https:<span class="comment">//api.github.com/repos/45145936/pinglun/issues?labels=Gitalk,cf1b9bedf8abfdc34802bcf9d9cde839&amp;t=1591326997341</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><br>   这个网址始终返回404 not found. 也就是说，程序找不到相应的Repostory来创建issues，仓库地址错误！那么我于此得来灵感，我建的新仓库<code>pinglun</code>不可能出错，只可能是前面的那串数字错了，但是api.github.com返回的ID也没有错，那我看了别人的设置，把自己的github_ID也换成名称串，跟owner一样，再试就成了<p></p>
<h1 id="xxx"><a href="#xxx" class="headerlink" title="xxx"></a>xxx</h1><p>xxx. 未完待续</p>
<script>
